Revision history for Cache-File-Simple

0.3 2026-06-25
	- Fix crash in cache() on corrupt/empty JSON cache files
	- Fix crash in cache_clean() when encountering empty or malformed cache files
	- Fix POD typo: DEFAULT_EXPIRES → DEFAULT_EXPIRE
	- Extract _cache_path() helper to eliminate duplicated hash-to-path logic
	- Only mkdir on cache set, not every cache() call
	- Fix numeric key 0 being silently hashed as empty string
	- Remove unused File::Basename import

0.2 2025-05-15
	- Add has_cache(), delete_cache(), cache_clean() functions

0.1 2025-05-15
	- Initial version
